headline: Lennox Unveils Elite Series EL18KSLV Side Discharge Heat Pump Designed for Compact Homes
summary: Lennox Residential HVAC, industry-leader in home comfort solutions, announced the launch of the Elite Series EL18KSLV Side Discharge Heat Pump, combining efficient performance and space-saving design.
